Doke-Purpose: Ingest Doke runtime plugins, MIME types, fonts, and client rects surface presets.
Doke-Subsystem: chrome/app startup command-line handling.
Doke-Detection-Target: CreepJS plugins, MIME types, fonts, and client rects consistency checks.
Doke-Rollback: Remove this patch from patches/chromium/series and rebuild Chromium; DokeBrowser will keep writing surface presets but Chromium will ignore them.

